title: Lombardi’s Week 12 Reactions | GM Street (Ep. 353)
description:
The Texans get their eighth straight win, this time on 'Monday Night Football,' Blake Bortles gets benched, Hue Jackson doesn’t get a handshake, and this week’s awards.

Hosts: Michael Lombardi and Tate Frazier
